reviewText: I love John Wayne, so getting to see him in his old movies for me is fun. I especially love him in True Grit and The Shootist! The DVDS are in great condition no problem with that. I just not sure i liked having all the DVDS stacked on top of each other. But i have now a special case for my DVDS so not an issue. Now i need to get his other movie "The Quiet Man!"
What can I say? John Wayne was bigger than life and these movies are no exception. Arguably one of a kind and movies under his belt that no one can duplicate in roles, he's truly an Icon.
Very happy with product and shipping
I Love It.  I Love John Wayne.
